WEBVTT

00:10:59.680 --> 00:11:03.680
And it turns out that this
is more prevalent in girls than boys.

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:05.776
At this young age,

00:11:05.800 --> 00:11:09.096
kids tend to mimic same-sex adults,

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:10.656
and at least in the US,

00:11:10.680 --> 00:11:14.600
over 90 percent of our elementary
school teachers are women.

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:19.040
Of course, it's not just
what happens in the classroom.

00:11:19.720 --> 00:11:22.736
Social media plays a big role here, too.

00:11:22.760 --> 00:11:24.536
It wasn't so long ago

00:11:24.560 --> 00:11:27.576
that you could purchase a Teen Talk Barbie

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:29.056
that when the cord was pulled,

00:11:29.080 --> 00:11:30.776
it would say things like,